data.title: Underneath the Paramount Hotel: The Diamond Horseshoe Story (Short 2014)
data.meta_description: Underneath the Paramount Hotel: The Diamond Horseshoe Story: Directed by Jesse David Harris. The documentary film which tells the amazing and untold story of the most famous nightclub in New York City. The jewel that was Billy Rose's Diamond Horseshoe is revealed in this personal and riveting story, told by performers who starred on stage, and a cigarette girl who worked the floor some 70 years ago.
